 } } \right.$$<br><br>$$ \therefore $$ $$\int\limits_0^3 {(g(x) - f(x))dx} $$<br><br>$$ = \int\limits_0^3 {g(x)dx}  - \int\limits_0^3 {f(x)dx} $$<br><br>$$ = \int\limits_0^2 {| - x|dx}  + \int\limits_2^3 { - (x - 4)dx}  - \int\limits_0^2 { - (x - 2)dx}  - \int\limits_2^3 {(x - 2)dx} $$<br><br>$$ = \int\limits_0^2 {x\,dx}  - \int\limits_2^3 {(x - 4)dx}  + \int\limits_0^2 {(x - 2)dx}  - \int\limits_2^3 {(x - 2)dx} $$<br><br>$$ = \left[ {{{{x^2}} \over 2}} \right]_0^2 - \left[ {{{{x^2}} \over 2} - 4x} \right]_2^3 + \left[ {{{{x^2}} \over 2} - 2x} \right]_0^2 - \left[ {{{{x^2}} \over 2} - 2x} \right]_2^3$$<br><br>$$ = 2 - \left\{ {{9 \over 2} - 12 - 2 + 8} \right\} + \{ 2 - 4\}  - \left\{ {{9 \over 2} - 6 - 2 + 4} \right\}$$<br><br>$$ = 2 - \left\{ {{9 \over 2} - 6} \right\} - 2 - \left\{ {{9 \over 2} - 4} \right\}$$<br><br>$$ = 10 - {9 \over 2} - {9 \over 2} = {{20 - 9 - 9} \over 2} = {2 \over 2} = 1$$

